```
class ModuleA{
    @Provides
    @Named(&quot;stringA&quot;)
    fun provideString() = &quot;&quot;
    /*
    other providers
     */
}

class ModuleB{
    @Provides
    @Named(&quot;stringB&quot;)
    fun provideString() = &quot;&quot;
    /*
    other providers
     */
}
```
Please note, that you have to use same qualifier in the injection site


